	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=122873><span id=Guru>Phreda the Hand</span></a><br><b><span id=Guru>Guru</span></b><br><span id=notbold>208 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Fascinating!&nbsp;&nbsp;All of that information was news to me!  Nektulos looks just like Misty Thicket, but there's obviously a lot more going on in there.  I'd like to try some of those ghouls, but not if the prize is eternal servitude to Evil!<br><br>I don't have a beef with the Drow so far... actually I think you folks are pretty.  Some humans are better than others in terms of agility, charm, and intelligence.  But the ones who decide fealty to Innoruuk is a good idea don't seem to be blessed with much!<br><br>Um, thanks but no thanks, I'd rather not become a slave.... I'll keep my eyes peeled for able-bodied recruits though, and send them your way. Heh heh.</p>&nbsp;<br>Phreda Biggles, 46 Warrior <br>Inebriator for the Order of the Keg <br><a href=HTTP://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/journal.html?user=122873 target=_new>Tales of a Halfling Tank Girl</a></td></td></tr>
