	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Sat, Jan 19th 4:15 PM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=122873><span id=Guru>Phreda the Hand</span></a><br><b><span id=Guru>Guru</span></b><br><span id=notbold>208 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [5.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Hands sore from new claws, won't write much - <br><br>Met Wormorf, Dwarf Warrior, in Highpass Hold; he sold me 2nd set of claws!&nbsp;&nbsp;They look awesome!  They are slower than the other claws.  Much easier now to slice and dice monsters.  Phanny loves to watch claws in action.  Also looted nice chainmail coif from gnolls, old headpiece now in bank.  New one looks just like Phanny's.  We match almost head to toe!  I like that.<br><br>Didn't notice when someone cast Spirit of Wolf on me, and accidentally ran smack into rock wall.  How embarrassing!<br><br>We left Highpass to meet Spelwithe, Phanny's Barbarian friend in Rivervale.  He has interesting tattoos on his head.  We gave him almost a full suit of looted gnoll ringmail, since he only had a kilt to wear.  He made trek from Halas to RV alone.  We showed him around town; he had a hard time getting through doors!  hee hee<br><br>Went to Gorge but it was empty.  Then we tried Runnyeye cave.  It used to be dangerous, but now it's too easy! We cleaned it out quick.  We found stairs going down, and might venture down there after we break camp.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sat Jan 19 15:22:44 2002</em></p>&nbsp;<br>Phreda Biggles, 46 Warrior <br>Inebriator for the Order of the Keg <br><a href=HTTP://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/journal.html?user=122873 target=_new>Tales of a Halfling Tank Girl</a></td></td></tr>
